headline: Labour Codes trigger showdown, Unions call ‘combative resistance’ on Nov 26
synthesis: This ties into broader market movement and sentiment.

timeline.text: The impending showdown over the Labour Codes highlights an escalating tension between unions and government authorities. With unions advocating for “combative resistance,” this conflict could significantly influence labor relations and economic stability. Observers should monitor how this unrest interacts with market dynamics and overall public sentiment in the coming weeks.
